name: Emergency
descrption: Ibn Sina Hospital operates one of the best Accident & Emergency Centre of Bangladesh with 6 beds.Services of Emergency Medicine:Trauma and non-trauma medical and surgical emergencies round the clock at the ground floor in level-1 of the hospital with a separate entrance.

name: Stroke ICU with full support
descrption: Stroke Unit, IBN SINA Hospital, under direct supervision of Prof. M. A. Hayee, who is the pioneer in Neuro-Intervention in Bangladesh, provides neurological treatment for the patients with diversified number of neurological disease like diseases of brain (stroke/infection), diseases of spinal cord etc.

name: MRI
descrption: Most of the human body is made up of water molecules, which consist of hydrogen and oxygen atoms.At the centre of each hydrogen atom is an even smaller particle called a proton. Protons are like tiny magnets and are very sensitive to magnetic fields.

name: X-ray
descrption: An X-ray is a quick, painless test that produces images of the structures inside your body — particularly your bones. X-ray beams pass through your body, and they are absorbed in different amounts depending on the density of the material they pass through.

name: CT-SCAN
descrption: Computed tomography (CT) scan is a useful diagnostic tool for detecting diseases and injuries. It uses a series of X-rays and a computer to produce a 3D image of soft tissues and bones. CT is a painless, noninvasive way for your healthcare provider to diagnose conditions

name: ENDOSCOPY
descrption: An endoscopy is a procedure where organs inside your body are looked at using an instrument called an endoscope. An endoscope is a long, thin, flexible tube that has a light and camera at one end. Images of the inside of your body are shown on a television screen.

name: Pain and Physiotherapy Center
descrption: The Burden of Pain never again is the motto of Ibn Sina pain physiotherapy and rehabilitation (rehab.) center. We offer the approach best of pain relief, physical therapy and medical care through appropriate medical consultancy, modern physiotherapy and rehabilitation services.

name: Diabetes center
descrption: Diabetes (Diabetes Mellitus) is classed as a metabolism disorder. Metabolism refers to the way our bodies use digested food for energy and growth. Most of what we eat is broken down into glucose. Glucose is a form of sugar in the blood. It is the principal source of fuel for our bodies.

name: Dental Center
descrption: Ibn Sina Dental Center is one of the most modern dental centers in Dhaka. Ibn Sina Dental center ensures experienced Dental Surgeon, modern and disinfected equipment, trained dentist for Children. All possible investigation including OPG and dental x-ray are performing at same center.
